OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny showers
OL,6,Fslowly dying out this evening. Then
OL,7,Fthe rest of the night will be dry with
OL,8,Fvariable amounts of cloud. A chilly
OL,9,Fnight with patchy frost.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FMost of the day will be dry
OL,12,Fand bright. Outbreaks of rain will
OL,13,Fspread into Argyll by late afternoon
OL,14,Fand elsewhere in the evening.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FSome
OL,17,Frain in the early hours of Monday
OL,18,Fotherwise it will be dry and bright.
OL,19,FBright spells and a few showers early
OL,20,Fand late on Tuesday. Scattered showers
OL,21,Fon Wednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
